column12:
'desc': [u'

Bukowski Lazy Morten - Cuddle bag (Brown) Price: Rs.545

Let your baby cuddle this little puppy to sleep. Very soft to touch and made from the finest of materials. A truly wonderful huggable animal for your baby brought to you from one of the best designers in Sweden - Barbara Bukowski. It has plastic beans inside in order to give more weight and feeling to the bear. The beans are secured in inner net bags and don't fall out even if the seam would break. The plastic beans are round and bigger than 2mm in three dimensions according to european security standards. The Bukowski bears are generally filled with polyester foam which is repellant to moister. This makes them dry faster after washing. The materials are syntethic in order to minimize the establishment of germs and damp when the bear becomes wet. It also makes the washing easier and minimizes the risk of allergy. All products are washable in 30 degrees handwash. All materials are flameproof without any flameobstructive chemicals. All eyes are secured and locked
column13: attached with a secure lock on the inside. Every baby item has eyes
column14:
mouth and nose embroidered by hand. \n
\n ']
